{"tid":25364,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"粗腰Baby凸肚置地嘆茶 曉明壯臂護妻","createTime":"2016-12-06T05:41:38.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T17:36:12.000Z","uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7db17362ba7347ba68863a31b5c9126855db0d6f","tid":25364,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:41:38.000Z","msg":"今日近中午時份，約11點40分左右，現身中環置地，據知佢哋係啱啱飲完茶出嚟，佢哋一行5、6人，其中包括曉明男助手同經理人Kim等，另有兩名操普通話嘅女子跟尾。<br />\n<br />\n曉明男助手一直喺前面護航開路，曉明兩公婆繼續以黑色夫婦裝示人，黑超黑帽黑褸，不過今日曉明有着白T恤同白鞋。除咗主角夫婦外，其他人神色都帶緊張，相信係怕逼親大肚Baby，但反而Baby全程表現友善，向記者揮手示意，老公曉明就出手攬實老婆，佢都係任影，但就提醒記者唔好閃親Baby，非常nice！（其實你哋兩公婆咁恩愛咪仲閃&hellip;&hellip;）<br />\n<br />\n佢哋一行人入咗商廈，但冇幾耐發現去錯地方，好彩佢哋好快搵得番要去嘅地方，就係咁，佢哋一齊消失於商廈。<br />\n<br />\n到中午一點二十分左右，兩公婆拖住手仔返落樓。問Baby預產期大約係幾時？Baby只係揮揮手，匆匆上七人車離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56010408&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161206\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56010408%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161206&d=gxWz%2FC6C71p60fUhkgd6dAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=d3efcc53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56010408%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161206&h=ae22d88c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56010408&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161206</a>"},{"pid":"d3e1c24646297be5320a15c1d28db63fb6d9056e","tid":25364,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46598a666858af8d8f8293760a9436bd4623eca0","tid":25364,"uid":25189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:56:01.000Z","msg":"你<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"abd99b9fb1841435a96517e284e4f21b8d101c1e","tid":25364,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11799cb788f90374512b85cb1bd7947b8f803fd7","tid":25364,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:15:51.000Z","msg":"樣子巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec545304bd6ed5b02c34812cd2dd878b00be357","tid":25364,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T17:31:37.000Z","msg":"屌，死返大陸生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ca7b17bc23efc161ce08c1a7db56f2d913d38f","tid":25364,"uid":33424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T17:36:12.000Z","msg":"樣子巴過左黎未"}]}